'''梅根·玛丽·凯利'''（{{lang-en|'''Megyn Marie Kelly'''}}，{{bd|1970年|11月18日}}），<ref>{{cite web| url= http://tvnewsroom.org/biography-images/megyn-kelly-7637/| title= Megyn Kelly: Biography and Images| website= TVNewsroom.org| accessdate= 28 August 2015| archive-date= 2015-11-19| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20151119143200/http://tvnewsroom.org/biography-images/megyn-kelly-7637/| dead-url= no}}</ref><ref name=elle1 />曾用名'''梅根·肯德尔'''（{{lang|en|Megyn Kendall}}），<ref>{{cite news |url = http://time.com/70888/megyn-kelly-2014-time-100/|title = The 100 Most Influential People: Megyn Kelly|work = [[时代杂志|Time]]|date = April 23, 2014|first = Brit|last = Hume|authorlink = |archivedate = February 1, 2015|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150201004507/http://time.com/70888/megyn-kelly-2014-time-100/|deadurl = no}}</ref>是美国一位新闻记者、主播、新闻和政治评论人，她曾经还是一位律师。2004年至2017年间在[[福克斯新闻频道|福克斯新闻频道]]工作，2017年起加入[[NBC新闻|NBC新闻]]。2013至2017年间，凯利每周一至周五在福斯新闻频道的[[纽约|纽约]]总部主持新闻类节目《凯利档案》（{{lang|en|''The Kelly File''}}）；在此之前她则主持另一档新闻节目《直播美国》（{{lang|en|''America Live''}}）；之前还曾与[[比尔·海默|比尔·海默]]共同主持新闻谈话节目《美国新闻室》（{{lang|en|''America's Newsroom''}}）。2007年至2012年间，凯利与海默合作一同主持了福斯新闻频道的[[跨年|跨年夜]]特别节目《全美新年》（{{lang|en|''All American New Year''}}）。2014年，《[[时代_(杂志)|时代]]》杂志将凯利评选为“全球最有影响力的百大人物”之一。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://time.com/70888/megyn-kelly-2014-time-100/ |title=Time 2014 100 Most Influential People |publisher=Time.com |date=April 23, 2014 |accessdate=April 29, 2014 |archive-date=2015-02-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150201004507/http://time.com/70888/megyn-kelly-2014-time-100/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2016年，凯利还成为了《[[名利场_(杂志)|名利场]]》杂志的封面人物。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.vanityfair.com/news/2015/12/megyn-kelly-fox-news-cover-story|title = Blowhards, Beware: Megyn Kelly Will Slay You Now|accessdate = 2016-01-22|author = Evgenia Peretz|date = 2016-01-31|publisher = Vanity Fair|archive-date = 2016-05-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160508114935/http://www.vanityfair.com/news/2015/12/megyn-kelly-fox-news-cover-story|dead-url = no}}</ref>

==早年生活和教育==
凯利出生于[[纽约州|纽约州]][[锡拉丘兹_(纽约州)|雪城]]，<ref name=syracusepoststandard>{{cite news | title= Syracuse native Megyn Kelly proves women can have it all on Fox News' 'The Kelly File' | url= http://www.syracuse.com/entertainment/index.ssf/2013/10/megyn_kelly_fox_news_syracuse_women_have_it_all.html | work= The Post-Standard | location= Syracuse, New York | date= October 6, 2013 | first= Geoff | last= Herbert | accessdate= June 2, 2015 | archivedate= 2014-02-23 | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140223030646/http://www.syracuse.com/entertainment/index.ssf/2013/10/megyn_kelly_fox_news_syracuse_women_have_it_all.html | deadurl= no }}</ref>父亲爱德华·凯利（{{lang|en|Edward Kelly}}）在[[紐約州立大學奧本尼分校|紐約州立大學奧本尼分校]]教授教育学，母亲琳达（{{lang|en|Linda}}）是一位家庭主妇。<ref name="elle1">{{cite news|url = http://www.elle.com/life-love/society-career/megyn-kelly-on-her-childhood|title = How Fox's Megyn Kelly Got to the Top, And Why She's Probably There to Stay|date = January 20, 2014|first = Ben|last = Dickinson|work = [[ELLE|Elle]]|accessdate = June 2, 2015|archivedate = May 26, 2015|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150526184342/http://www.elle.com/culture/career-politics/interviews/a12652/megyn-kelly-profile/|deadurl = no}}</ref>凯利的母亲有意大利血统。<ref name=elle1/> 

凯利9岁时随全家一同搬到纽约州[[奥尔巴尼|奥尔巴尼]]郊区的{{le|德尔玛 (纽约州)|Delmar, New York|德尔玛}}居住，<ref name=syracusepoststandard />之后她也在这里完成了高中学业。<ref name=nytimesmagazine>{{cite news| url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/01/25/magazine/the-megyn-kelly-moment.html| title=The Megyn Kelly Moment| first=Jim| last=Rutenberg| date=January 21, 2015| work=The New York Times Magazine| accessdate=June 2, 2015| archivedate=2015-06-02| archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6YzkgYm6x?url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/01/25/magazine/the-megyn-kelly-moment.html?_r=0| deadurl=no}}</ref>凯利15岁时，她的父亲逝世，母亲也随后改嫁。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://alb.merlinone.net/mweb/wmsql.wm.request?oneimage&imageid=6546634 |title=For Megyn Kelly, a quick rise at Fox |publisher=''[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]'' via ''Times Union'' (Albany, New York)|date=April 16, 2008|first=Howard|last=Kurtz |accessdate=November 29, 2012| archivedate= June 2, 2015| archiveurl = http://www.webcitation.org/6Yzhltfi5 | deadurl=no}}</ref> 

高中毕业后，凯利进入[[雪城大学|雪城大学]]学习，获得[[政治学|政治学]]学士学位，<ref name=elle1/>之后又就读[[奥尔巴尼法学院|奥尔巴尼法学院]]，在1995年获得[[法律博士|法律博士]]学位。<ref>{{cite web |title=Fact Sheet > Select Prominent Alumni |url=http://www.albanylaw.edu/about/pages/facts.aspx |publisher=Albany Law School |location=Albany, New York |accessdate=November 10, 2012 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150722025413/http://www.albanylaw.edu/about/pages/facts.aspx |archivedate=2015-07-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

==事业==
=== 律师 ===
凯利曾在[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]的{{lang|en|Bickel & Brewer}}[[律师事务所|律师事务所]]担任律师，这期间在[[美国律师协会|美国律师协会]]期刊《{{lang|en|Litigation}}》上发表了文章《律师担任董事的利益冲突角色》（{{lang|en|''The Conflicting Roles of Lawyer as Director''}}）。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://heinonline.org/HOL/LandingPage?collection=journals&handle=hein.journals/laba23&div=16&id=&page= |title=23 Litigation 1996–1997 Conflicting Roles of Lawyer as Director, The Conflicts |publisher=Heinonline.org |date= |accessdate=August 13, 2011 |archive-date=2017-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170422021915/http://heinonline.org/HOL/LandingPage?collection=journals&handle=hein.journals%2Flaba23&div=16&id=&page= |dead-url=no }}</ref>之后她又进入{{le|众达律师事务所|Jones Day}}工作了九年，她的客户包括信息服务公司{{le|益博睿|Experian}}等企业。<ref>{{cite web|title=ZARY MAREKH, on behalf of herself and others similarly situated, Plaintiff-Appellant, v. EQUIFAX; EXPERIAN, formerly, TRW; TRANS UNION,, (2nd Cir. 2001)|url=http://federal-circuits.vlex.com/vid/zary-marekh-herself-equifax-experian-trw-18531486|access-date=2016-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160202120441/http://federal-circuits.vlex.com/vid/zary-marekh-herself-equifax-experian-trw-18531486|archive-date=2016-02-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

=== 新闻 ===
==== 早期事业 ====
2003年，凯利搬到了[[华盛顿特区|华盛顿特区]]，成为[[美国广播公司|美国广播公司]]旗下电视台WJLA-TV的一名记者。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://alb.merlinone.net/mweb/wmsql.wm.request?oneimage&imageid=6546634 |title=Times Union – Albany NY |publisher=Alb.merlinone.net |date=April 16, 2008 |accessdate=August 13, 2011 |archive-date=2016-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160620043638/http://alb.merlinone.net/mweb/wmsql.wm.request?oneimage&imageid=6546634 |dead-url=no }}</ref>在华盛顿工作期间，凯利参与了诸多重大事件的报道，包括[[華盛頓特區狙擊手攻擊事件|華盛頓特區狙擊手攻擊事件]]和[[2004年美国总统选举|2004年美国总统选举]]等重大新闻。<ref name="foxnews1"/>2004年，凯利向[[福斯新闻频道|福斯新闻频道]]华盛顿分部寄了一段自己的录像，希望能加入该频道。她这段录像中报道新闻的方式和政治观点打动了福斯新闻频道资深记者{{le|布里特·休姆|Brit Hume}}，凯利自此开始成为该频道驻华盛顿特区记者。<ref name="foxnews1">{{cite news|url=http://www.foxnews.com/on-air/personalities/megyn-kelly/bio/#s=h-l|title=Megyn Kelly – Biography|publisher=Fox News|accessdate=November 10, 2012|date=January 13, 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151118021541/http://www.foxnews.com/on-air/personalities/megyn-kelly/bio/#s=h-l|archive-date=2015-11-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="WashPost"/><ref name=NYT/>

==== 福斯新闻频道 ====
之后凯利加入福斯新闻频道的节目《布里特·休姆特别报道》（{{Lang|en|''Special Report with Brit Hume''}}），负责其中法律板块的内容，并在《周末直播》（{{Lang|en|''Weekend Live''}}）中主播自己的法律板块《凯利法庭》（{{Lang|en|''Kelly's Court''}}）。她每周还在[[比尔·奥莱利|比尔·奥莱利]]的节目《奥莱利实情》（{{Lang|en|''The O'Reilly Factor''}}）的固定板块中登场，有时亦会替其他新闻主播主持节目，但一般是周末节目的代班主播。此外她还曾与[[比尔·海默|比尔·海默]]共同主持新闻谈话节目《美国新闻室》（{{lang|en|''America's Newsroom''}}）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newsmax.com/TheWire/megyn-kelly-five-things-fox/2013/07/05/id/513541/|title=Megyn Kelly: Five Things to Know About Fox News' Rising Star|work=NewsMax|date=2013-07-15|accessdate=2016-01-22|archive-date=2016-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160302225240/http://www.newsmax.com/TheWire/megyn-kelly-five-things-fox/2013/07/05/id/513541/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="WashPost">{{cite news |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/04/13/AR2008041302158.html |first=Howard |last=Kurtz |title=Megyn Kelly, Fox News's Fast-Rising Anchor |publisher=Washingtonpost.com |date=April 14, 2008 |accessdate=August 13, 2011 |archive-date=2016-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160206072600/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/04/13/AR2008041302158.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>2010年2月1日，凯利开始主持自己本人的下午一点档两小时节目《直播美国》（{{Lang|en|''America Live''}}）。她还是晚间政治讽刺节目《与格雷戈·古特费尔德一起熬夜》（{{Lang|en|''Red Eye w/ Greg Gutfeld''}}）的客串讨论成员。2010年，凯利的《直播美国》比前一年同一时间段节目的总收视人数提高了20%，这也是福斯新闻频道11月最高的同比收视增幅。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.businessinsider.com/megyn-kelly-sees-biggest-year-to-year-ratings-increase-at-fox-news-2010-11 |title=Megyn Kelly Sees Biggest Year to Year Ratings Increased at Fox News |publisher=Business Insider |date=2010-11-30 |accessdate=November 30, 2010 |archive-date=2016-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160204160537/http://www.businessinsider.com/megyn-kelly-sees-biggest-year-to-year-ratings-increase-at-fox-news-2010-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>凯利在福斯新闻参与了[[2008年美国总统选举|2008年美国总统选举]]和[[2010年美国中期选举|2010年美国中期选举]]的报道，以及[[美国最高法院大法官|美国最高法院大法官]][[塞繆爾·阿利托|塞繆爾·阿利托]]和[[约翰·罗伯茨|约翰·罗伯茨]]的确认听证会、[[2010年墨西哥灣漏油事故|2010年墨西哥灣漏油事故]]等重大新闻的报道。她还主持报道了大法官[[索尼娅·索托马约尔|索尼娅·索托马约尔]]和[[艾蕾娜·卡根|艾蕾娜·卡根]]的确认听证会。<ref name="foxnews1"/>

2012年，凯利参与了[[2012年美国总统选举|2012年美国总统选举]]的新闻报道。她在这期间表现出众，获得了媒体的广泛关注。<ref name="foxnews1"/>2012年11月6日开票当晚，凯利与[[布雷特·拜尔|布雷特·拜尔]]共同主播开票特别报道节目。部分投票结果揭晓后，亲[[共和党_(美国)|共和党]]的福斯新闻频道做出预测，认为[[民主党_(美国)|民主党]]总统候选人[[贝拉克·奥巴马|贝拉克·奥巴马]]将成功连任。直播期间，共和党政治人物[[卡尔·洛夫|卡尔·洛夫]]却在直播现场坚决反对这一预测结果，认为共和党候选人[[米特·罗姆尼|米特·罗姆尼]]仍有获胜机会。凯利对此回应道：“是不是你作为一名共和党人，这样算会让自己感觉好一点？还是（罗姆尼）真的（有获胜机会），你真的这么认为？”随后她在直播中走到演播厅外的福斯新闻选情预测中心，确认了预测结果。这一系列举动获得了媒体的关注，也被认为是她事业的一大亮点。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/fox-megan-kelly-on-karl-rove-projections-2012-11|title=Fox Anchor Megyn Kelly Asks Karl Rove An Awkward Question About His Projections|work=Business Insider|date=2012-11-06|accessdate=2016-01-22|archive-date=2016-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160129052321/http://www.businessinsider.com/fox-megan-kelly-on-karl-rove-projections-2012-11|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=NYT>{{cite news |last=Dowd |first=Maureen |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/11/11/opinion/sunday/dowd-romney-is-president.html?src=ISMR_AP_LO_MST_FB |title=Romney Is President |work=The New York Times |date=November 10, 2012 |accessdate=November 29, 2012 |archive-date=2008-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080225062850/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/11/11/opinion/sunday/dowd-romney-is-president.html?src=ISMR_AP_LO_MST_FB |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mediaite.com/tv/karl-rove-causes-fox-news-chaos-by-challenging-obama-victory-projection/|title=Karl Rove Causes Fox News Chaos By Challenging Obama Victory Projection|work=Mediaite|date=2012-11-07|accessdate=2016-01-22|archive-date=2016-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160129192753/http://www.mediaite.com/tv/karl-rove-causes-fox-news-chaos-by-challenging-obama-victory-projection/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年7月，凯利因[[产假|产假]]离开《直播美国》。10月回归后开始主持自己的直播时事分析节目《凯利档案》（{{Lang|en|''The Kelly File''}}），每周一至周五晚21点播出。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.adweek.com/tvnewser/in-17-years-fnc-has-made-5-evening-changes-cnn-and-msnbc-have-made-75/198165?red=tn |title=In 17 Years, FNC Has Made 5 Evening Changes; CNN and MSNBC Have Made 75 - TVNewser |publisher=Mediabistro.com |date=September 17, 2013 |accessdate=November 6, 2013 |archive-date=2015-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208135323/http://www.adweek.com/tvnewser/in-17-years-fnc-has-made-5-evening-changes-cnn-and-msnbc-have-made-75/198165?red=tn |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Hasselbeck ditching 'The View' for 'FOX and Friends'|url=http://pagesix.com/2013/07/09/hasselbeck-ditching-the-view-for-fox-and-friends/|publisher=NY Post|accessdate=July 10, 2013|archive-date=2016-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160220045400/http://pagesix.com/2013/07/09/hasselbeck-ditching-the-view-for-fox-and-friends/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

