anta Is White' Remarks"] {{Wayback|url=http://m.stuttgartdailyleader.com/article/20131214/NEWS/312149985 |date=20181026222744 }}, ''[[TV_Guide|TV Guide]]'' via ''Stuttgart Daily Leader'' (December 14, 2013).</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://nation.foxnews.com/2013/12/21/megyn-kelly-addresses-white-santa-comments|title=Megyn Kelly Addresses 'White Santa' Comments|work=Fox News|date=2013-12-21|access-date=2016-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160206071855/http://nation.foxnews.com/2013/12/21/megyn-kelly-addresses-white-santa-comments|archive-date=2016-02-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

