08 |accessdate=August 13, 2011 |archive-date=2016-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160403160421/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/03/16/fashion/weddings/16vows.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.douglasbrunt.com/about-doug-brunt/|title=Douglas Brunt biography|accessdate=July 1, 2013|archive-date=2016-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160215171138/http://douglasbrunt.com/about-doug-brunt/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Fox News' Megyn Kelly delivers baby boy |last1=Green |first1=Stephanie |last2=Glover |first2=Elizabeth |newspaper=The Washington Times |publisher=News World Communications |url=http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2009/sep/25/fox-news-megyn-kelly-delivers-baby-boy/ |date=September 25, 2009 |accessdate=April 29, 2013 |archive-date=2015-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150722025116/http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2009/sep/25/fox-news-megyn-kelly-delivers-baby-boy/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1377068/Fox-News-anchor-Megyn-Kelly-gives-birth-baby-girl.html |title=Fox News anchor Megyn Kelly gives birth to baby girl |date=April 15, 2011 |work=Mail Online |agency=Associated Newspapers |accessdate=April 29, 2013 |location=London |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305024557/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1377068/Fox-News-anchor-Megyn-Kelly-gives-birth-baby-girl.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

凯利认为自己在政治上是独立选民，称自己此前给[[民主党_(美国)|民主党]]和[[共和党_(美国)|共和党]]两党都投过票。权威人士则认为她在社会议题上偏向[[自由主义|自由派]]，在财政议题上则偏向[[保守主义|保守派]]。她认为自己不偏向于任意党派，因此能在报道新闻时更高效。<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://variety.com/2015/tv/news/fox-news-megyn-kelly-independent-1201525083/|title = Fox News Anchor Megyn Kelly Comes Out as an Independent|accessdate = 2016-01-22|author = |date = 2015-06-22|publisher = Variety|archive-date = 2015-10-19|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151019062205/http://variety.com/2015/tv/news/fox-news-megyn-kelly-independent-1201525083/|dead-url = no}}</ref>

